description:
*Losing My Religion?: Our Response to Marty Sampson* | In August 2019, former Hillsong band member, Marty Sampson, announced that he is no longer a Christian. On his Instagram page, Sampson listed some questions and reasons for his shaky faith and we at Little Light Studios decided to take a crack at answering them through the lens of the Bible. Having doubts about the Christian faith isn't anything new and isn't something to be ashamed of. The danger comes from isolation, pride, and a misunderstanding of the divine love of Jesus Christ. We hear you Marty...let's talk about it. @hillsong @hillsongworship @hillsongunited
